{"type":"message","id":"9153576d","parentId":"d15beb93","timestamp":"2026-02-27T17:41:49.601Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，目录创建成功。现在让我创建 SKILL.md 文件和一个 Python 脚本来生成 PPT。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:5","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\nname: pptx\ndescription: \"Generate PowerPoint presentations (.pptx) programmatically. Use when: user asks to create a presentation, generate slides, make a PowerPoint, export slides, or create a deck. NOT for: editing existing .pptx files or complex animations. Requires: python-pptx library.\"\nmetadata: { \"openclaw\": { \"emoji\": \"📊\", \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"python3\"], \"python_packages\": [\"python-pptx\"] } } }\n---\n\n# PPTX Skill - PowerPoint Generator\n\nGenerate professional PowerPoint presentations programmatically.\n\n## When to Use\n\n✅ **USE this skill when:**\n- \"Create a presentation about...\"\n- \"Generate slides for...\"\n- \"Make a PowerPoint deck\"\n- \"Export this to .pptx\"\n- \"Create a pitch deck\"\n- \"Make a slideshow\"\n\n❌ **DON'T use this skill when:**\n- Editing existing .pptx files (not supported yet)\n- Complex animations or transitions needed\n- Need to extract text from existing PPTs\n\n## Quick Start\n\n```bash\n# Generate a simple presentation\npython3 ~/work/openclaw/skills/pptx/scripts/generate_pptx.py \"My Title\" \"output.pptx\"\n```\n\n## Python API\n\nUse `python-pptx` library:\n\n```python\nfrom pptx import Presentation\nfrom pptx.util import Inches, Pt\nfrom pptx.dml.color import RgbColor\nfrom pptx.enum.text import PP_ALIGN, MSO_ANCHOR\n\n# Create presentation\nprs = Presentation()\n\n# Add slide with title layout\nslide_layout = prs.slide_layouts[0]  # 0 = title slide\nslide = prs.slides.add_slide(slide_layout)\ntitle = slide.shapes.title\nsubtitle = slide.placeholders[1]\n\ntitle.text = \"Hello World\"\nsubtitle.text = \"My Presentation\"\n\n# Add content slide\ncontent_layout = prs.slide_layouts[1]  # 1 = title + content\nslide = prs.slides.add_slide(content_layout)\ntitle = slide.shapes.title\ntitle.text = \"Agenda\"\n\ncontent = slide.placeholders[1]\ntf = content.text_frame\ntf.text = \"First point\"\n\np = tf.add_paragraph()\np.text = \"Second point\"\np.level = 1  # Indent\n\n# Save\nprs.save('output.pptx')\n```\n\n## Slide Layouts\n\n| Index | Layout |\n|-------|--------|\n| 0 | Title slide |\n| 1 | Title + Content |\n| 2 | Section header |\n| 3 | Two content |\n| 4 | Comparison |\n| 5 | Title only |\n| 6 | Blank |\n| 7 | Content with caption |\n| 8 | Picture with caption |\n\n## Common Patterns\n\n### Add Bullet Points\n\n```python\ntf = shape.text_frame\ntf.text = \"First bullet\"\n\nfor item in [\"Second\", \"Third\", \"Fourth\"]:\n    p = tf.add_paragraph()\n    p.text = item\n    p.level = 0\n```\n\n### Add Image\n\n```python\nleft = Inches(1)\ntop = Inches(2)\nheight = Inches(4.5)\npic = slide.shapes.add_picture('image.png', left, top, height=height)\n```\n\n### Format Text\n\n```python\nfrom pptx.util import Pt\nfrom pptx.dml.color import RgbColor\n\np = tf.paragraphs[0]\np.font.size = Pt(24)\np.font.bold = True\np.font.color.rgb = RgbColor(0, 0, 128)  # Navy blue\n```\n\n### Add Table\n\n```python\nrows, cols = 3, 2\nleft = Inches(2)\ntop = Inches(2)\nwidth = Inches(6)\nheight = Inches(3)\n\ntable = slide.shapes.add_table(rows, cols, left, top, width, height).table\n\n# Set column headers\ntable.cell(0, 0).text = \"Name\"\ntable.cell(0, 1).text = \"Value\"\n```\n\n## Installation\n\n```bash\npip3 install python-pptx\n```\n\n## Example: Full Presentation\n\n```python\nfrom pptx import Presentation\nfrom pptx.util import Inches, Pt\n\nprs = Presentation()\n\n# Title slide\nslide = prs.slides.add_slide(prs.slide_layouts[0])\nslide.shapes.title.text = \"Q4 Results\"\nslide.placeholders[1].text = \"Company Overview\"\n\n# Content slide\nslide = prs.slides.add_slide(prs.slide_layouts[1])\nslide.shapes.title.text = \"Key Metrics\"\ncontent = slide.placeholders[1].text_frame\ncontent.text = \"Revenue up 25%\"\n\np = content.add_paragraph()\np.text = \"User growth: 10K new users\"\np = content.add_paragraph()\np.text = \"Retention: 85%\"\n\nprs.save('q4_results.pptx')\n```\n","file_path":"~/work/openclaw/skills/pptx/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":319,"output":1237,"cacheRead":17920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19476,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772214089640}}
