{"type":"message","id":"5b31c095","parentId":"49bff8d6","timestamp":"2026-02-27T17:43:25.440Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！PPT 生成成功了。现在让我验证技能是否被 OpenClaw 识别。我需要检查一下 OpenClaw 是否能看到这个新技能。让我也测试一下用 JSON 输入的复杂演示文稿。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"完美！技能已创建并测试成功！让我演示一下完整功能："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:17","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /tmp/demo_slides.json << 'EOF'\n{\n  \"title\": \"AI 产品介绍\",\n  \"subtitle\": \"2026年度规划\",\n  \"slides\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"产品概述\",\n      \"content\": [\n        \"基于大语言模型的智能助手\",\n        \"支持多模态交互\",\n        \"私有化部署方案\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"核心功能\",\n      \"content\": [\n        \"自然语言对话\",\n        \"代码生成与调试\",\n        \"文档分析与总结\",\n        \"多语言翻译\"\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"技术架构\",\n      \"content\": [\n        \"前端：React + TypeScript\",\n        \"后端：Python FastAPI\",\n        \"模型：自研大语言模型\",\n        \"部署：Docker + K8s\"\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}\nEOF\npython3 ~/work/openclaw/skills/pptx/scripts/generate_pptx.py --json /tmp/demo_slides.json /tmp/demo.pptx && ls -lh /tmp/demo.pptx"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":181,"output":336,"cacheRead":24576,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25093,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772214195868}}
