{"type":"message","id":"5e041318","parentId":"e040e874","timestamp":"2026-02-27T18:08:59.826Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"openclaw CLI 没有安装。让我直接检查配置文件中是否有 Telegram 相关的设置。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**问题找到了：**\n\n你的 Telegram 凭证存在（`~/.openclaw/credentials/telegram-*`），但：\n1. **配对请求是空的**（`\"requests\": []`）- 意味着没有待处理的配对\n2. 可能之前尝试配对但没完成，或者 Bot 配置有问题\n\n---\n\n## 🔧 解决方案\n\n### 选项 1：检查现有 Bot 配置\n你之前是否配置过 Telegram Bot？如果有：\n- **Bot Token** 是否正确？\n- **Webhook** 是否设置？\n\n### 选项 2：重新设置 Telegram\n如果需要重新配置，我可以帮你：\n1. 去 [@BotFather](https://t.me/botfather) 创建/获取 Bot Token\n2. 配置 Webhook\n3. 完成配对流程\n\n---\n\n**你现在的情况是：**\n- ✅ Webchat（这里）—— 正常工作\n- ❓ Telegram —— 配置可能不完整\n\n**能告诉我你的 Telegram Bot Token 吗？**（或者去 @BotFather 获取一个）\n\n或者，**你想先确认一下其他配置是否正确？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":319,"output":248,"cacheRead":40192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40759,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772215733457}}
