{"type":"message","id":"2d7af767","parentId":"946511f6","timestamp":"2026-02-27T18:10:22.673Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Token 已经存储好了。现在需要在配置文件中添加 Telegram provider 配置。但是 OpenClaw 可能需要重启 Gateway 或者需要 webhook 配置才能生效。\n\n让我更新 config.yaml 添加 telegram 配置。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在更新配置文件添加 Telegram provider："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:79","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > ~/.openclaw/config.yaml << 'EOF'\n# OpenClaw 配置文件\n# 位置: ~/.openclaw/config.yaml\n\nskills:\n  load:\n    # 额外的 skill 目录\n    extraDirs:\n      - /Users/lvze/work/skills/skills\n\n    # 监视 skill 文件夹变化\n    watch: true\n    watchDebounceMs: 1000\n\n# Telegram 配置\ntelegram:\n  enabled: true\n  # Bot Token 存储在 credentials/telegram-bot-token.json\n  webhook:\n    enabled: true\n    # 使用本地 webhook URL，需要配合 ngrok 或类似工具\n    url: null  # 启动后会自动配置\nEOF\necho \"配置已更新\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":463,"output":231,"cacheRead":40704,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41398,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772215813069}}
