{"type":"message","id":"6066f362","parentId":"5b56853a","timestamp":"2026-02-27T18:10:31.725Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"配置已更新。但是要让 Telegram Bot 真正工作，还需要：\n1. 设置 webhook URL（需要一个公网可访问的 URL）\n2. 启动/重启 OpenClaw Gateway\n3. 完成配对流程\n\n由于用户可能正在运行 OpenClaw Gateway，我应该告诉他需要重启服务，并且需要配置 webhook。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **Token 已安全存储！**\n\n---\n\n## 📋 配置完成\n\n**已添加：**\n- ✅ Bot Token → `~/.openclaw/credentials/telegram-bot-token.json`\n- ✅ Telegram provider 配置 → `~/.openclaw/config.yaml`\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 接下来需要做的\n\n### 1. 重启 OpenClaw Gateway\n配置更改后需要重启服务才能生效：\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n### 2. 配置 Webhook（关键！）\nTelegram Bot 需要**公网可访问的 webhook URL**。\n\n**选项 A：使用 ngrok（本地开发）**\n```bash\nngrok http 8080  # 假设 OpenClaw 运行在 8080 端口\n```\n然后将生成的 https URL 配置到 `config.yaml` 的 `telegram.webhook.url`\n\n**选项 B：如果你已有域名**\n直接配置你的公网 URL\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 检查当前 Gateway 状态\n\n能运行这个命令吗？\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway status\n```\n\n或者告诉我：\n1. **你是在本地运行 OpenClaw 吗？**\n2. **有公网 IP 或域名吗？**\n3. **还是需要用 ngrok 做内网穿透？**\n\n这样我可以帮你完成最后的 webhook 配置 🐾"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":457,"output":347,"cacheRead":40960,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41764,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772215822688}}
